        "timestamp": "2020-07-03 10:14:04.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\n> Patch Set 1:\n> \n> I am not sure. We will update the documentation for Guilin and I believe there will be major changes.\n\nWell, we can update this part when those changes are finalized. I do think it's better to leave this here and not just link to somewhere else, the ONAP documentation is convoluted enough as it is. :D",
